"villager after the other disappared, some moved away. After a long night "
"with no sleep, he decided it was time for him to leave as well. With nothing"
" to live off, he was desperate to | Curious to all the villagers, it seemed "
"%name% lost his interest in the woods with time, speaking of going away "
"every more often if he spoke at all. One fateful day, they saw him volunteer"
" to | One fateful day a tree he fell slew a deer. %name% did not want to "
