"him a faith-shattering question, %name% abandoned his faith, seeking out "
"spirituality by other means. | Unfortunately, prayer did not spare his "
"brothers from a slaughter. %name% realized that his faith was better "
"invested in looking out for himself than muttering to some so-called god. | "
